LINE.Text: SocialLife is a regular Harris Interactive survey tracking UK social media use. It offers the most
comprehensive insights available on the UK social media scene.
There has been lots of positive news for Instagram, the Facebook-owne photo and video
sharing service, in recent weeks with one survey revealing nearly 35 million monthly users in
the US alone equating to double-digit growth in a 12 month period.
Many are predicting that Instagram will soon catch up with Twitter in usage and engagement
levels and another survey cited Instagram as US teens' preferred social network.
